{"id": "1931", "post": "<div class=\"post-1931 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-virtual-servers tag-canada tag-servarica-com tag-xen\" id=\"post-1931\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/servarica-6-99-256mb-xen-vps-in-canada/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Servarica \u2013 $6.99 256MB Xen VPS in Canada</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/canada/\" rel=\"tag\">canada</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/servarica-com/\" rel=\"tag\">servarica.com</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/xen/\" rel=\"tag\">xen</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> June 27, 2011 @ 4:01 am, by LowEndAdmin</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><a href=\"http://servarica.com/\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/images/servarica.jpg\" data-src=\"/media/images/servarica.jpg\" class=\"screenshot litespeed-loaded\" alt=\"Servarica\" data-was-processed=\"true\"></a> Hani from <a href=\"http://servarica.com/\"><b>Servarica</b></a> emailed me their special package for LowEndBox readers. Their 1 Share instance starts at $10/month, with <a href=\"http://www.webhostingtalk.com/showthread.php?t=1059887\">this code posted on WHT</a> you can get it for $8/month, but if you are happy with less disk space and less monthly data, you can <a href=\"https://servarica.com/clients/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=81\">sign up this package</a> for <b>$6.99/month</b>.</p><ul><li>256MB memory</li><li>8GB storage</li><li>250GB/month data transfer on 100Mbps</li><li>Citrix XenServer</li></ul><p>Servers with <a href=\"http://www.netelligent.com/\">Netelligent</a> in Montreal Canada (tes